g.text: Stay on top of tasks & collaborate with ease
A New Level ofTeam Collaborationand Performance
Simplify and Amplify Your Critical Business Systems

An Operational System of Record creates a foundational, interconnected platform for your tech stack that improves data insights and provides all the key capabilities you need to successfully operate your services organization in the modern, service level economy. The result—a fully-integrated enterprise solution designed specifically for your services business.

An increase of on-time, on-budget projects, and transparent collaboration gives clients more of what they want for higher satisfaction rates. Inviting clients to participate on the platform increases client engagement, alignment, and accountability, which contributes to strong relationships and success.
